rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0002
rows.name:
Kisasa has been training to become a legendary
salvager, to be praised and admired, mo.

rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0003
rows.name:
But the other day, when I had Mochimochi
judge my salvaging skills...

rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0004
rows.name:
I was told I was even worse than a complete
amateur salvager apprentice, mo!

rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0005
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling kind=Anger ]Come to think of it, Kisasa has only been training
and has never actually done any salvaging, mo!

rows.label: tlk42340111_03_msg0006
rows.name:
[ML:Feeling ]To become a legendary salvager, it seems I need
to do a lot of salvaging and recover a lot
of treasure, mo.
